</figure>
</section>
<section id="fs-idm337789072" class="section-summary">
<title>Summary</title>
<para id="fs-idm347658720">Once you become an entrepreneur, you can consider giving back to the entrepreneurial community by becoming a mentor, consultant, or champion to support other people in their ventures.</para>
</section>
