<title>Review Questions</title>
<exercise id="fs-idm336626736">
<problem id="fs-idm351290752">
<para id="fs-idm355161264">Acting as a mentor provides ________.</para>
<list id="fs-idm336659776" list-type="enumerated" number-style="upper-alpha">
<item>expert assistance to the venture startup team and self-growth for the mentor</item>
<item>opportunities to diminish relationships</item>
<item>the mentor with professional development</item>
<item>the mentee with peer recognition</item>
</list>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idm340602432">
<problem id="fs-idm338128176">
<para id="fs-idm338140576">A serial entrepreneur is someone who ________.</para>
<list id="fs-idm335971760" list-type="enumerated" number-style="upper-alpha">
<item>wants to retire</item>
<item>creates a pattern of starting multiple ventures</item>
<item>plans for a low stress future</item>
<item>plans to start the first venture</item>
</list>
</problem>
</exercise>
